"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**If the world is getting a new currency, will it be led by CBDCs, a permissionless blockchain like Bitcoin or a permissioned chain such as Diem?**\\n\\nI think for a period of time, we are going to have all of the above. \\n\\nSome countries like [China are strongly pursuing](https://cointelegraph.com/news/china-s-cbdc-is-about-domestic-dominance-not-beating-the-dollar) the CBDC route, which gives them more surveillance and control over their economy and population. They’ll have a greater ability to surveil transactions, block transactions, automatically debit people’s accounts based on infractions or their social credit score, and program money so that it can only be used in certain places or certain times. It will also give them the ability to go around the SWIFT system, to give them more control over their international commerce with some of their trading partners. \",\"timestamp\":1639216085,\"title\":\"ransmission tower by the Yangtze River in Wuhu, East China's\"},\"digest\":\"MLsksc1HdI93lidUjnSCmFazxA_HzzONhjva1Vys8mk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x7DF054391F98b4a261cF4668dedeA77587F0f5a5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"QFxcmQiTBCQ-xcXXVtIV52Erj4QyD7psWMUXY5BZpJo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"myDYx23h_ReUvX4NC2gW-9h9IYNIPPve1XOdzhL5a5w\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Sn5hTibkbULnTv4xNysyJMTdBzmiKn0ixkoGZLH3RfLfT-1hLAyHK4vFuLlmD5HC9qjWIvuarkbXVok5p6ajKA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xfce38e4cbeb90e5116ab551ec50b89404c8ba374022935c04e0031639d4a2c2e1b7962aa495d08f1d610f2a6cdf801417acb94c25d2a6f33a5b8d155b866a74e1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"QFxcmQiTBCQ-xcXXVtIV52Erj4QyD7psWMUXY5BZpJo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"myDYx23h_ReUvX4NC2gW-9h9IYNIPPve1XOdzhL5a5w\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"